    section#commo
      .container.vh-75
        .row.align-items-center.h-100
          .col-md-6.align-self-center
            img(src="assets/ship.png", alt="", srcset="").img-fluid
          #commo-text.col-md-6.align-self-center
            h4 CIF to any seaport in the world. We are connected to the largest suppliers of animal protein in the South and North and we also work with sugar, soybeans, rice, Yellow Corn, oils and agricultural inputs for export. 
            p foreign trade specialist of grains and agricultural inputs, animal protein, energy and mining.
            a.btn.btn-primary See Our Products
            
    section#our-products
      .container.vh-100
        .h-100.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.flex-column
          h3.text-center Our Products
          mixin card(title, copy, button)
            .card
              .content
                h2.title= title
                p.copy= copy
                button.btn= button

          main.page-content
            each card in cards
              +card(card.title, card.copy, card.button)
            
            
    section#video
