            p Our challenge is to participate in the market in a competitive way, honouring our commitments and always seeking our clients' satisfaction.
            a.btn.btn-primary See Our Products
          .col-md-6.align-self-center.d-flex.justify-content-center
            video#player(playsinline='' controls='' data-poster='')
              source(src='/assets/video.webm' type='video/webm') 

